<p>Who&#8217;s Blake Ross?  Seriously, that&#8217;s what I asked (I forgot his name, it turns out).</p>

<p>In response to your AS v. BR thing, I can only say&#8212;it&#8217;s not a competition, man!  Pursue the work you find interesting, and don&#8217;t worry about what other people are doing.  Firefox is an interesting and important product.  RSS is an interesting an important spec.  You&#8217;re doing cool stuff, so stop worrying the small stuff (and magazine covers are, in fact, small stuff).</p>

